50|$|An ion-induced <b>dipole</b> <b>force</b> {{consists}} of an ion and a non-polar molecule interacting. Like a dipole-induced <b>dipole</b> <b>force,</b> the charge of the ion causes distortion of the electron cloud on the non-polar molecule.|$|E
